+
+## Environment Variables
+
+### Required
+
+| Variable         | Description                              |
+|-----------------|------------------------------------------|
+| `DATABASE_URL`  | PostgreSQL connection string             |
+
+### Optional (Server-side defaults)
+
+| Variable          | Default            | Description                          |
+|-------------------|--------------------|--------------------------------------|
+| `SERPAPI_KEY`     | None               | Default SerpAPI key (users can override via BYOK) |
+| `GOOGLE_API_KEY`  | None               | Default Gemini key (users can override via BYOK)  |
+| `GEMINI_MODEL`    | `gemini-2.5-flash` | Gemini model ID                      |
+| `ARTICLE_LIMIT`   | `3`                | Default max articles per run         |
+| `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` | `*`                | CORS origins                         |
+| `DB_POOL_SIZE`    | `5`                | Connection pool size                 |
+| `DB_MAX_OVERFLOW` | `10`               | Max burst connections                |
+
+### Docker Compose `.env` Example
+
+```env
+POSTGRES_USER=admin
+POSTGRES_PASSWORD=admin
+POSTGRES_DB=cddbs
+DATABASE_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://admin:admin@db:5432/cddbs
+SERPAPI_KEY=your_key_here
+GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_key_here
+GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
+ARTICLE_LIMIT=3
+```
